version_description:
Following the requests was added:
<br>Music system, select Music from the Music App and listen to it in your in-game car. (Need to download music to the Iphone / Ipad by Itunes);
<br>Clothing store on the map so you can change the look of the character;
<br>New car color changing system with more color choices;
<br>Car headlamp running;
<br>Camera filters for the game;
<br>Day / Night added;
<br>Neon in cars;
<br>LED in the car sound box;
<br>New car added;
<br>10 new wheels for you to choose;
<br>Various customization options for the character;
<br>4 new sound box;
<br>Sound of opening and closing door and trunk in all cars;
<br>Sound of the honking of cars running;
<br>New camera option for character;
